sentences.en: Only identified by his surname Wang, he is said to have received about $3,000 for his kidney.

sentences.en: Wang Cunchun, 90, lives with his 60-year-old son in a 107-square-foot apartment in Shanghai, China.

sentences.en: "Import growth is a bit higher than we expected, showing that domestic demand is still resilient," said Mr Wang.

sentences.en: "The problem of overweight and obesity is rising sharply as the dietary make-up has changed," Wang Guoqiang, a vice director of commission, told a press conference.
